    "description": "<p>Founded in 2024, our Singapore-based executive search firm is on a mission to forge impactful partnerships and drive progress. We believe that matching the right talent with the right opportunity transforms both careers and organizations.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Empower Partners offer tailored solutions, including retained searches, contingency options, project consulting, interim staffing, market research, and compensation advisory.</p>\n<p>Empower Partners excel in functional hires across banking, asset management, private wealth, payments &amp; fintech, insurance &amp; insurtech, family office, education, energy &amp; renewables and professional services and consulting.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Beyond our deep understanding of Singapore, we harness our internal expertise and research capabilities to drive successful searches across Asia, Dubai, the Middle East, and the US.</p>\n<p>You can find out more about us at https://empowerpartners.sg/</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Empower Partners Search Pte Ltd is part of the CGP Group of Companies.</p>",
